description: 808 Renewable Energy Corporation, through its subsidiaries, engages in the design, development, manufacture, distribution, and marketing of general aviation and electric vehicles in the United States. It offers AR-1 gyrocopter and electric reverse-trike vehicles under the Dagger, Arrow, and Orca names through distributors and dealers. The company was formerly known as Tri-Energy Corporation and changed its name to 808 Renewable Energy Corporation in August 2021. 808 Renewable Energy Corporation was incorporated in 2009 and is based in Bradenton, Florida.
